overview:
Sembox is a SEM ad agency, based in Lodz.

It offers sponsored links advertising campaigns at Polish and foreign search engines. Sponsored links are the most efficient and cheapest way of advertising on the Internet as you pay solely per clicks and for leading the user to the website that sells specific products or services. Sembox offers creating, configuration and optimization of sponsored link campaigns. For Google Adwords campaigns Sembox offers sponsored links in the search results, in the contextual net, on youtube and mobile devices. Owing to a great number of options in which the links are displayed, the ad reaches the target group. Visit Sembox.pl to find out a number of valuable information and practical advice on sponsored links.
